data.description: Enjoy spacious living with room for everyone! This 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom abode boasts ample space, featuring a roomy basement with abundant storage and two bonus rooms. Nestled in the Beaver Glen neighborhood, residents enjoy a plethora of amenities, including a community pool, clubhouse, playground, picnic pavilion, tennis courts, and basketball courts. Upon entry through the front door, you're greeted by the inviting living room, adorned with a soaring 2-story ceiling and a loft view from the upper level. Convenience is key with the Owner's Suite conveniently located on the main level, complete with a luxurious private bathroom featuring a soaking tub, double walk-in closets, and a separate shower. Ascend the stairs to discover four additional bedrooms and two full bathrooms, with one bedroom serving as a secondary suite equipped with its own private bathroom—ideal for overnight guests or in-laws. Situated less than 5 miles from Robins AFB, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on all this home has to offer—call today to schedule a private showing!
